Place frappe-gantt assets here for offline/restricted environments.

Supported filenames the app will try to serve:
- frappe-gantt.umd.js  (preferred UMD build)
- frappe-gantt.min.js  (minified build)

Get them from a trusted machine:
- https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/frappe-gantt/dist/frappe-gantt.umd.js
- https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/frappe-gantt/dist/frappe-gantt.min.js

Do not commit truncated files. Verify the file ends with a proper IIFE closure (e.g., `return S});`).
